  <question type="essay">
    <name>
      <text>Media, variância e desigualdade de probabilidade.</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>Seja <img class="latex" src="https://chart.googleapis.com/chart?cht=tx&amp;chf=a,s,000000|bg,s,FFFFFF00&amp;chl=X" alt="X" /> uma variável aleatória discreta com suporte <img class="latex" src="https://chart.googleapis.com/chart?cht=tx&amp;chf=a,s,000000|bg,s,FFFFFF00&amp;chl=%5Cchi%3D%5C%7B-c%2Cc%5C%7D" alt="\chi=\{-c,c\}" /> onde <img class="latex" src="https://chart.googleapis.com/chart?cht=tx&amp;chf=a,s,000000|bg,s,FFFFFF00&amp;chl=c" alt="c" /> é uma constante positiva. e função de probabilidade dada por</p>
<p><img class="latex" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://chart.googleapis.com/chart?cht=tx&amp;chf=a,s,000000|bg,s,FFFFFF00&amp;chl=f(x)%20%3D%20%5Cbegin%7Bcases%7D%0A0%2C5%2C%26%20%5Ctext%7Bse%20%7Dx%3D-c%2C%5C%5C%0A0%2C5%2C%26%20%5Ctext%7Bse%20%7Dx%3Dc%2C%5C%5C%0A0%2C%26%20x%5Cnot%5Cin%20%5Cchi.%0A%5Cend%7Bcases%7D" alt="f(x) = \begin{cases}
0,5,&amp; \text{se }x=-c,\\
0,5,&amp; \text{se }x=c,\\
0,&amp; x\not\in \chi.
\end{cases}" /></p>
<p>Calcule <img class="latex" src="https://chart.googleapis.com/chart?cht=tx&amp;chf=a,s,000000|bg,s,FFFFFF00&amp;chl=E(X)" alt="E(X)" />, <img class="latex" src="https://chart.googleapis.com/chart?cht=tx&amp;chf=a,s,000000|bg,s,FFFFFF00&amp;chl=%5Csigma%5E2(X)" alt="\sigma^2(X)" /> e cheque que <img class="latex" src="https://chart.googleapis.com/chart?cht=tx&amp;chf=a,s,000000|bg,s,FFFFFF00&amp;chl=P(%5C%7CX%20-%20E(x)%5C%7C%5Cleq%20c)%20%3D%20%5Cfrac%7B%5Csigma%5E2(X)%7D%7Bc%5E2%7D" alt="P(\|X - E(x)\|\leq c) = \frac{\sigma^2(X)}{c^2}" />.</p>]]></text>
    </questiontext>
